## Air Bag Module Inspection  


Inspect the air bag module by using an ohmmeter can deploy the air bag module, which may cause serious injury. Do not use an ohmmeter to inspect the air bag module. Always use the on- board diagnostic function to diagnose the air bag for malfunctions. (Refer to 08- 01 AIR BAG SYSTEM ON- BOARD DIAGNOSIS.)  

